    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban use of isolation booths in schools",
        "additional_details": "My son is suffering terribly as a result of this.\r\n \r\nChildren can suffer mental health issues due to this disgusting punishment... especially those on the Autistic spectrum..\r\n \r\nIt's inhumane to shut a child away in an isolation booth for a day at a time with little outside contact and limited toilet breaks, as some schools have done.\r\n \r\nThis needs to stop now.",
        "background": "Ban the use of isolation booths as punishment in all schools. It\u2019s barbaric and cruel, especially to those on the autistic spectrum.",
